{Speech 13 Answer 49}{}{All right, then let me ask a question.}
{Speech 13 Answer 49*}{}{Well, I already got that I'm a moron. Can I ask you something instead?}
{Speech 13 Answer 40}{}{Moron? Me, a moron? Listen, pal, that's how you get into big trouble, got it?}
