{Speech 14}{}{Paying for everyone? Well, damn, that's something... You owe 35 coins.}
{Speech 14 Answer 6}{}{Money's bullshit. Beer for everyone!}
{Speech 14 Answer 6*}{}{Vuz, buddy, I'm paying for beer for everyone! These guys are just great!}
{Speech 14 Answer 6**}{}{Vuz, come here. Are you my friend or not? Hic. These guys are my best pals, give everyone another bottle on me.}
{Speech 14 Answer 6***}{}{Vuz! Beer for everyone, I'm paying!}
{Speech 14 Answer 25}{}{Well, come to think of it, I must've gone completely crazy buying beer for some rotten idiots.}
{Speech 14 Answer 12}{}{No way, I'd better just buy a drink for myself.}
{Speech 15}{}{Oh! I've got a tale for you! You'll piss yourself laughing. So, picture a head...}
{Speech 15 Answer 42}{}{A head?}
